  "notes": "Philosophy:\nAttack and raze realms.\nNo phase 3 cards because of Gib Igoy.\n\nEvents:\nMany battle helping cards with duration for use with Rule: The Event Wheel.\n\nRulings:\nhttp://oracle.wizards.com/scripts/wa.exe?A2=ind0408B&L=SPELLFIRE-L&P=R5015&I=-3\nNo heroes can be instantly defeated by any card,  Living  wall, Scroll or nasty spells, even wish.\n\nIf Morcanth defends against a Dragon, that dragon returns to their pool and the battle is over.\nhttp://oracle.wizards.com/scripts/wa.exe?A2=ind9810B&L=SPELLFIRE-L&P=R4115&I=-3\n\nCombos:\n-Tergoz plays Tsuki Kotegaeshi, if cards drawn are allies, they cannot be played.\n-Net of Entrapment on champ, then play Tsuki Kotegaeshi for same effect\n-Ego Coin on Gib Occav so he can pull artifacts of any world from discard piles\n-Tyrinon let's Trium Allies Fly with him, so does Pretty Magical Ring\n-4th/152 Ambush followed by CQ/022 Concussing Blow",
